data.description: Beautiful condo in the desirable Playa Del Sol community. Features open floor plan at kitchen and living room level, with beautiful cabinets, countertops and a large island with dining seating, upgrades abound with stainless steel appliances, (that convey), walk-out covered patio, and tons of natural light. All bedrooms are located on the third floor, with a owner-suite connected to the ensuite bathroom, with shower, dual vanities, and a walk-in closet. Full size stackable washer and dryer are located upstairs in a dedicated closet, which will convey. The home features an attached 2-car garage. The Playa Del Sol community features include a gated community, pool, spa, clubhouse.
